|ID|OPERATOR             |NAME       |EST.ROWS|EST.TIME(us)|
------------------------------------------------------------
|0 |MERGE                |           |3       |6           |
|1 |└─HASH JOIN          |           |3       |6           |
|2 |  ├─TABLE FULL SCAN  |T1         |3       |3           |
|3 |  └─SUBPLAN SCAN     |T2         |4       |3           |
|4 |    └─TABLE FULL SCAN|SOURCETABLE|4       |3           |
============================================================
